commit message:
Noop change. Tried to figure out why scrolling in TimeTable is so slow, but
even without the gallery and the list overlapping it is, while other
ScheduleListViews are not.
Add the ability to hide talks/tracks/rooms. There's no unhide feature yet!
Fix null pointer dereference in new getTracks() function.

When deleting an item while in SearchActivity, don't revert to superclass
behaviour (i.e. suddenly show a block schedule or something again).

Add the ability to recover hidden items (using the context menu in the
chooser).

0.99.9 - Because version numbers don't mean anything (also, this is how I
should've called the previous release already..)
